lead_paragraph: Britain's Danny Willett kept his nerve to win the Dubai Desert Classic by a stroke from compatriot Andy Sullivan and Spain's Rafa Cabrero-Bello on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Willett Keeps His Nerve to Win Dubai Desert Classic
